{"tid":590591,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"毒呢樣野根本係天生","createTime":"2018-03-12T18:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T01:48:18.000Z","uid":94266,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8eecbb26c7649c4e7c7b137d5c6532546823c342","tid":590591,"uid":94266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:38:16.000Z","msg":"自問打扮普通，唔會太毒。<br />\n性格上，都唔會話得罪人，講錯野。<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解，中學以黎，啲人就從來唔會搵我玩，最多只係起班上吹吓水就算。<br />\n<br />\n試過兩次叫班friend出黎（起大學，唔係同一班），但係都叫唔郁。反而單獨叫出黎，就叫到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦，到出黎做野，什至做義工，都成日畀人放我飛機。我真係唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解？<br />\n<br />\n已經好難唔相信毒係天生呢樣野。仲有就係命運呢樣野。我真係好想打破佢地。"},{"pid":"c476faf9edc0220f9422f73405b7b7109dec29fb","tid":590591,"uid":94266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9220abafc3668bf458b39990ad2472f97f076dd1","tid":590591,"uid":59705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0b6ce058edb83f8a7b8262d9f6db9f9efab61e","tid":590591,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T18:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/025235_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim